1
00:00:13,839 --> 00:00:15,560
Let's see if your fists are faster

2
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:18,559
or my gun.

3
00:00:23,879 --> 00:00:24,559
Wang Wenhao

4
00:00:25,519 --> 00:00:26,879
What you wanted is right here

5
00:00:28,719 --> 00:00:30,039
Now let Ruo Jin go

6
00:00:30,320 --> 00:00:30,960
No!

7
00:00:34,119 --> 00:00:35,439
Saving the damsel, huh?

8
00:00:36,039 --> 00:00:37,000
Fine, fine, fine

9
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:39,920
Today, I'll let you play the hero

10
00:00:41,679 --> 00:00:43,359
I won't do anything to Ruo Jin

11
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:47,679
After all, our wedding's just around the corner

12
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:49,280
Wang Wenhao

13
00:00:50,679 --> 00:00:52,000
Cut the crap

14
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,920
If you've got the guts, come at me

15
00:00:55,479 --> 00:00:57,039
Using a woman to threaten me

16
00:00:58,719 --> 00:01:01,039
You're a spineless coward

17
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,920
Tie him up, now!

18
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:11,239
No!

19
00:01:14,719 --> 00:01:15,280
Search him

20
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:17,319
Gu Yuan

21
00:01:18,439 --> 00:01:18,959
Gu Yuan

22
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:20,799
Gu Yuan

23
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,319
Don't worry about us

24
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:23,560
Go help Feifan, quickly

25
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,719
Getting you to a safe place

26
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:25,840
is helping Feifan.

27
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:27,799
Don't worry

28
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,599
Once we get through this crisis

29
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,239
Premier Medical Hall

30
00:01:32,159 --> 00:01:33,040
you'll be back soon

31
00:01:41,799 --> 00:01:42,400
Feifan!

32
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:46,159
Feifan! Feifan! Feifan!

33
00:01:48,719 --> 00:01:49,439
Wang Wenhao!

34
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:52,760
The Wangs won't stay untouchable forever.

35
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:54,680
After a scene this big,

36
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:57,079
the police will track you down in no time.

37
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,000
Ruo Jin,

38
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:01,439
you're my fiancee.

39
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,400
If anything really goes down,

40
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,239
do you think you can escape?

41
00:02:07,799 --> 00:02:08,319
Feifan!

42
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,840
Feifan, don't listen to him!

43
00:02:10,439 --> 00:02:11,159
Ruo Jin,

44
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:12,840
get out of here!

45
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,240
Wang Wenhao,

46
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,919
you already have me tied up here.

47
00:02:19,599 --> 00:02:21,560
Why not just take Ruo Jin and leave?

48
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,919
Are you trying to die with me?

49
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,280
Ren Feifan,

50
00:02:27,879 --> 00:02:29,960
you eyesore.

51
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:33,400
Finally, you'll be out of my sight.

52
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:36,400
Oh,

53
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:37,680
by the way,

54
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,439
let me show you who this is.

55
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,039
Mommy, where are you?

56
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,000
Yixin!

57
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,039
Yixin!

58
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:50,840
When can I come play with you?

59
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:54,560
Let's go to the amusement park with Daddy.

60
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:57,080
Wang Wenhao,

61
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:59,000
what did you do to Yixin?

62
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,000
What did you do to Yixin?!

63
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,360
Ren Feifan,

64
00:03:10,719 --> 00:03:12,120
if you dare try anything funny,

65
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:15,360
I'll send Yixin down to keep you company.

66
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:19,759
Wang Wenhao,

67
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,680
don't make me kill you.

68
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:27,159
You want to kill me?

69
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,159
Come on!

70
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,000
Kill me!

71
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:33,680
Ren Feifan,

72
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:36,479
see you in the next life.

73
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:37,879
Feifan!

74
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,199
Move!

75
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,039
Feifan!

76
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,319
Feifan!

77
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,759
Let me go!

78
00:03:47,759 --> 00:03:48,159
Move!

79
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:51,000
Feifan! Feifan!

80
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,280
Feifan!

81
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:58,000
Hurry up and untie the ropes on my back!

82
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,319
Why didn't you wait until I was blown up?

83
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,719
I wish I could have.

84
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,520
Wang Wenhao, let me go!

85
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,479
Let me go!

86
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:08,560
I want to die! I want to die with Feifan!

87
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,400
I wanted you to watch him die

88
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,879
so you'd give up hope and just marry me.

89
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:13,400
Get her inside.

90
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,520
No! Let me go! Let me go!

91
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,399
Untie it faster!

92
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,240
We planned for everything,

93
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,680
but we still missed a step.

94
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:23,600
Let's go!

95
00:04:33,399 --> 00:04:33,720
Dad,

96
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,240
the biggest threat has now been eliminated.

97
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,800
You don't have to worry anymore

98
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:40,079
about anyone in North City toppling us.

99
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:42,800
But the old man from the Ren family

100
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,639
is still missing.

101
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:48,680
That means Ren Feifan had accomplices.

102
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:50,399
Come on, Dad,

103
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,759
you're overthinking it.

104
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:56,000
At most, they sensed danger and hid.

105
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:58,439
Maybe they've gone off the grid

106
00:04:58,959 --> 00:04:59,959
and will never come back.

107
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,680
Send someone to keep investigating.

108
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,920
I don't like leaving loose ends.

109
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:11,040
That temper of yours will get you killed one day.

110
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:13,680
Come on, Dad,

111
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,680
my wedding to Ruo Jin is right around the corner.

112
00:05:17,199 --> 00:05:17,920
Lighten up a little!

113
00:05:36,759 --> 00:05:37,399
Sit.

114
00:05:38,959 --> 00:05:39,639
Close your eyes.

115
00:05:40,399 --> 00:05:41,160
What is it?

116
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,160
Look.

117
00:05:47,319 --> 00:05:48,279
It's beautiful.

118
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:48,959
Do you like it?

119
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,680
I love it.

120
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:51,560
Let me put it on for you.

121
00:05:58,759 --> 00:05:59,399
It looks stunning.

122
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:03,879
I wish I could wear it on our wedding day too.

123
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,959
As my lady commands.

124
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,920
What are you doing here?

125
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,439
I came to see you.

126
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,920
White is unlucky.

127
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,879
Gemstones suit you better.

128
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:11,160
Does it look good?

129
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,480
Beautiful.

130
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,439
Xu Ruo Jin.

131
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:22,360
Are you here for the wedding, Miss Shen?

132
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,759
Others come bearing gifts.

133
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,160
You came to hand out slaps.

134
00:07:27,279 --> 00:07:28,079
What are you talking about?

135
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,839
Xu Ruo Jin.

136
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:32,560
Are you really going to marry him?

137
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:41,399
I'm marrying Wenhao because I love him.

138
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:42,199
I want to.

139
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,920
Miss Shen, if you're here for the wedding,

140
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:46,920
you're most welcome.

141
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,959
If not,

142
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:50,839
please leave.

143
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:56,199
I never thought you were this kind of person.

144
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,079
I was so wrong about you.

145
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:04,319
Miss Shen.

146
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,160
This way, please.

147
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,279
Ruo Jin.

148
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:21,800
Ruo Jin.

149
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:26,480
Feifan.

150
00:08:31,199 --> 00:08:34,120
Let me see if you're hurt anywhere.

151
00:08:34,279 --> 00:08:35,080
Ruo Jin, I'm fine.

152
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,120
Just listen to me first.

153
00:08:36,759 --> 00:08:38,480
Tomorrow, attend Wang Wenhao's wedding.

154
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:41,200
Then see which of his people aren't there.

155
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,919
Gu Yuan and I will track his movements.

156
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,840
We should be able to find Yixin's location.

157
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:48,879
Got it.

158
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:51,360
I'll play it by ear when the time comes.

159
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:59,480
The wedding is about to begin.

160
00:08:59,679 --> 00:09:01,639
Let's give a warm round of applause

161
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:03,399
to welcome the bride and groom.

162
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,679
Yes!

163
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,240
Happily united in marriage

164
00:09:22,879 --> 00:09:24,080
A hundred years of harmony

165
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,879
First, I'd like to thank everyone here

166
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:32,759
for attending my wedding with Ruo Jin.

167
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,559
Ruo Jin and I have been through so much together,

168
00:09:36,039 --> 00:09:37,559
and it wasn't easy getting to this day.

169
00:09:38,759 --> 00:09:40,200
So I want to say to Ruo Jin,

170
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:43,200
I promise to be a good husband,

171
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:44,799
and protect you for a lifetime.

172
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:49,679
Next, I want to thank my father.

173
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:52,440
Without his hard work in raising me,

174
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:55,080
there would be no Wang Wenhao today.

175
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,519
Finally,

176
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,200
I want to thank all of you here

177
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,600
for being here today

178
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:03,919
to witness a new start for the Wangs,

179
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,240
a new era.

180
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:09,159
In the near future, Wang Pharmaceutical

181
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:12,960
will launch a drug that'll stun the world.

182
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:16,480
Recently, some people got jealous,

183
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,799
coveting our new product,

184
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,679
constantly trying to sabotage it.

185
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,799
In the end, it was all in vain.

186
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,279
They only ended up hurting themselves.

187
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,960
If any of you here support us

188
00:10:27,559 --> 00:10:29,519
and partner with Wang Pharmaceutical,

189
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:32,679
we're willing to offer shares.

190
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,000
Besides getting a piece of the pie,

191
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:37,159
we can also give everyone here

192
00:10:38,399 --> 00:10:40,879
a chance to go down in history.

193
00:10:41,159 --> 00:10:42,039
Alright.

194
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:54,799
The groom may now kiss the bride.

195
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,200
Kiss her!

196
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,639
Kiss her!

197
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:03,600
How's the progress lately?

198
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,120
We're speeding it up.

199
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,000
Make sure to hurry.

200
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:07,799
Understood.

201
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,000
How could this be?

202
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:17,759
Who did this? How could anyone do this?

203
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:20,000
My God, this is outrageous!

204
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,440
So inhumane!

205
00:11:21,559 --> 00:11:23,320
Unbelievable, how cruel!

206
00:11:24,759 --> 00:11:26,440
How did these things end up here?

207
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,240
Isn't this a crime?

208
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,320
Someone!

209
00:11:28,519 --> 00:11:29,440
Shut it off!

210
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:31,919
Shut it off!

211
00:11:32,759 --> 00:11:34,240
So this is what you called

212
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:36,279
the new drug that would stun the world?

213
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:40,080
Ren Feifan!

214
00:11:45,919 --> 00:11:46,679
How can this be?

215
00:11:48,159 --> 00:11:48,600
How are you...

216
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,360
Still alive, right?

217
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:53,200
Wang Wenhao,

218
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:55,759
looks like your bomb didn't quite work.

219
00:11:57,559 --> 00:11:58,480
What are you saying?

220
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:00,639
I have no idea what you mean.

221
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:03,200
I showed up right at your moment of triumph.

222
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,720
Must be a tough pill to swallow, right?

223
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,639
As you can all see,

224
00:12:11,679 --> 00:12:14,440
this is how Wang Group developed the drug.

225
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:18,919
They kidnapped patients for live testing,

226
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:21,159
causing multiple deaths.

227
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:24,559
And their so-called miracle cure-all drug

228
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,759
actually has no such effect.

229
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:31,600
Don't believe him, everyone!

230
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,159
This is all fake!

231
00:12:33,159 --> 00:12:34,440
Everything he's saying is fake!

232
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:37,759
Seems young Mr. Wang still won't admit it.

233
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,200
That's alright.

234
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:41,000
I have more evidence.

235
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:42,519
Take a look.

236
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,960
These are all imported instruments.

237
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:51,039
Can you afford it if you break them?

238
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:52,799
Get back to work, all of you.

239
00:12:53,879 --> 00:12:55,679
Mr. Wang, the experiment next door is starting.

240
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:58,399
Radiation is high. You should step away.

241
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:03,519
The new drug developed by Wang Group

242
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:07,080
is an unfinished product from my youth.

243
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:09,600
After my parents talked to me,

244
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:12,440
I realized this drug is highly unstable

245
00:13:13,039 --> 00:13:15,600
and can cause severe side effects.
